format: A data frame with 6 observations on the following 4 variables.

parameters.dose: a numeric vector of doses applied
parameters.n: a numeric vector contained the total number of insects
parameters.log10dose: a numeric vector of logarithm-transformed doses
parameters.r: a numeric vector contained number of dead insects

reference: The log-logistic model provides an inadequate fit.
title: Deguelin applied to chrysanthemum aphis

Description
